public interface Indexable

A view of the indexes in an Indexed content container.

Convenience object to access an Index over some subset of indexes from an Indexed container.

Nested Class Summary

          An empty Indexable, that always yield an empty iterator.

          A sequence iterable, that returns a Sequence iterator, iterating on the indexes in an array.
static class Indexable.Singleton
          A singleton iterable, that returns a Singleton iterator, iterating on a single index.
